ke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cross w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 9a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a1 1 0 0 1-1 1z\"></path></svg><span>Faith-Based</span></div></div></div></section><nav class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-5\" aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-400\">/</li><li><a class=\"text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium\" href=\"/names/religion/christian/1\">Christian Names</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-400\">/</li><li class=\"text-blue-700 font-semibold\">Boy Names</li></ol></nav><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-blue-100 text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2\">100+</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Total Names</div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-blue-100 text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2\">40</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Biblical Names</div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-blue-100 text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2\">5</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Origins</div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg border border-blue-100 text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2\">2025</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Updated</div></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-blue-100\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6\">The Complete Guide to Christian Boy Names</h2><div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-4\"><p class=\"leading-relaxed\">Choosing a name for your baby boy is one of the most important decisions parents make. In Christian tradition, names carry deep significance and connect children to the rich heritage of Biblical history. Our collection features <strong class=\"text-blue-700\">100+ authentic Christian boy names</strong> with verified meanings, Hebrew &amp; Greek origins, and lucky numbers.</p><p class=\"leading-relaxed\">Each name in our database has been carefully researched to ensure accuracy of meaning and spiritual significance. Whether you&#x27;re looking for traditional Biblical names like Noah and Elijah, or modern favorites like Liam and Lucas, you&#x27;ll find the perfect name for your little one.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center\">Complete List of Christian Boy Names</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><a id=\"liam\" class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 p-6 border border-blue-100 hover:border-blue-300 group hover:-translate-y-1 block\" href=\"/names/christian/liam\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between mb-4\"><div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\">Liam</h3></div><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cross w-6 h-6 text-blue-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 9a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V