width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-cross w-6 h-6 text-blue-600\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 9a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a1 1 0 0 1-1 1z\"></path></svg></div></div><p class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-4\">&quot;<!-- -->Wood, forest<!-- -->&quot;</p><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Origin:</span><span>Latin</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Lucky Number:</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 rounded-full font-bold\">7</span></div></div></a></div></section><section class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-blue-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">What are the most popular Christian boy names?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">The most popular Christian boy names include Noah, Elijah, James, Benjamin, Michael, Daniel, Jacob, Samuel, Joseph, David, Matthew, and Gabriel. These names have deep roots in the Bible and Christian tradition, making them timeless choices for Christian families worldwide.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-blue-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">How do I choose a Christian name for my baby boy?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">When choosing a Christian name for your baby boy, consider the Biblical meaning, origin, and whether it has a connection to scripture. Names with positive meanings like &#x27;God is gracious&#x27;, &#x27;Gift of God&#x27;, or &#x27;God is my strength&#x27; are highly recommended in Christian tradition.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-blue-100\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">What Christian boy names mean &#x27;Gift from God&#x27;?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">Several Christian boy names carry the meaning &#x27;Gift from God&#x27;, including Matthew, Theodore, Nathan, and Mateo. These names express gratitude for the blessing of a child and are beloved choices among Christian families.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center\">Explore More Names</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-rose-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/christian/girl-names\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Christian Girl Names</h3><p class=\"text-pink-100 text-sm\">Browse 100+ Biblical girl names</p></a><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/names/religion/christian/1\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">All Christian Names</h3><p class=\"text-blue-100 text-sm\">Discover 15,000+ Christian names</p></a><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/islamic/boy-names\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Islamic Boy Names</h3><p class=\"text-emerald-100 text-sm\">Find 100+ Muslim boy names</p></a><a class=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 text-white rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1\" href=\"/guides/expert-naming-guide\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2